WEBVTT

00:00:06.995 --> 00:00:09.598
Which of these has 
the least carbohydrates?

00:00:09.598 --> 00:00:10.977
This roll of bread?

00:00:10.977 --> 00:00:12.327
This bowl of rice?

00:00:12.327 --> 00:00:14.224
Or this can of soda?

00:00:14.224 --> 00:00:15.380
It's a trick question.

00:00:15.380 --> 00:00:19.689
Although they may differ in fats,
vitamins, and other nutritional content,

00:00:19.689 --> 00:00:23.051
when it comes to carbs,
they're pretty much the same.

00:00:23.051 --> 00:00:26.323
So what exactly does that mean
for your diet?

00:00:26.323 --> 00:00:30.375
First of all, carbohydrate is 
the nutritional category for sugars